name: Anima - Miss Cupcake Responsive Sample File
description:
This file showcases an interactive high-fidelity prototype.


With Anima you can build high-fidelity prototypes and get HTML/CSS and React code.


Features included in this file:

  • Breakpoints
  • Video
  • Embed code (Google Maps)
  • Live form
  • Entrance animation
  • Hover effect


Be sure to install Anima to make this file come alive: www.animaapp.com
